Repository
New:       git init
Clone:     username@host:/path/to/repository
Pull:      git pull
History:   git log --pretty=oneline

Branches
Create:    git checkout -b <branch>
Delete     git branch -d <branch>
Switch     git checkout master
Diff       git diff <source-branch> <target-branch>

Add & remove Index
Status:    git status
Add file:  git add <file>
All all:   git add *
Remove:    git rm <file>

Commit & Push
Commit:    git commit -u "message"
Push:      git push origin <branch>

Merge & Tag
Merge     git merge <branch>
Tag       git tag <tag> <commit-ID>
